<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

        <section class="title-section text-center py-5">
            <h1 class="display-4">Local Pulse</h1>
            <p class="lead">Modern Solutions for Local Businesses</p>
        </section>

        <main class="container mt-5">
            <section>
                <div class="card mt-4">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2 class="card-title">Our Service</h2>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            &#8594; <strong>Website Creation</strong>: We craft stunning, user-friendly websites that
                            reflect your brand's unique identity and drive customer engagement. Whether you need a
                            simple landing page or a dynamic website, we've got you covered.<br>
                            &#8594; <strong>Reliable Hosting</strong>: Enjoy peace of mind with our secure and reliable
                            hosting solutions. We ensure your website is always online and running smoothly, so you can
                            focus on what matters most, growing your business.<br>
                            &#8594; <strong>Hassle-Free Experience</strong>: We handle all the technical details, making
                            the process seamless for you. From initial design to launch, we work closely with you to
                            ensure everything meets your expectations without any stress.<br>
                            &#8594; <strong>Low Cost</strong>: We believe that quality website solutions shouldn't break
                            the bank. We keep our costs as low as possible to ensure our pricing is low.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="contact-section py-5 text-center">
                <div id="contactForm" class="contact-form mt-4" style="display: block;">
                    <h2>Transform your Business Now</h2>
                    <form id="contactFormElement">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="name">Name / Business</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" placeholder="Name or business..."
                                required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="email">Email</label>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="Contact email..." required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="message">Message</label>
                            <textarea class="form-control" id="message" rows="3"
                                placeholder="Include any details or questions you may have..." required></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Send Message</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section>
                <div class="card mt-4">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2 class="card-title">About Us</h2>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            We are a locally based web development service proudly situated in Lisburn. I am an
                            inspiring Computer Science student at Queen's University Belfast, and passionate about
                            helping local businesses thrive in the digital landscape.
                            <br><br>
                            With a focus on modern solutions, we aim to provide high-quality website creation and
                            hosting services tailored to meet the unique needs of each client. We believe that every
                            business deserves a strong online presence, and we are dedicated to making that happen in a
                            hassle-free and affordable manner.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section>
                <div class="container py-5">
                    <h2 class="text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                    <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
                        <div class="card border">
                            <div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-link" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                                        data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                        <span class="arrow">&#8594;</span> What services do you offer?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne"
                                data-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    We provide customized website development designed specifically for local
                                    businesses, guaranteeing a smooth and captivating online experience.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card border">
                            <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                                        data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                        <span class="arrow">&#8594;</span> How long does it take to create a website?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo"
                                data-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    Thanks to our years of experience in website creation and the integration of AI
                                    technology, building a website has never been faster. While timelines can vary based
                                    on specific needs, a typical completion timeframe is around two weeks after we
                                    finalize the requirements.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card border">
                            <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                                        data-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false"
                                        aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                        <span class="arrow">&#8594;</span> Do you provide ongoing support?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree"
                                data-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    Absolutely! We provide continuous support and maintenance to keep your website
                                    running smoothly and up to date. Any requested changes will be implemented within a
                                    day, with even faster responses for urgent updates.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>

        <%- include('partials/footer') %>

</body>

<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
<script>
    $(document).ready(function () {
        // Handle form submission
        $('#contactFormElement').on('submit', async function (event) {
            event.preventDefault(); 

            const name = $('#name').val(); 
            const email = $('#email').val(); 
            const message = $('#message').val();

            const response = await fetch('/api/contact', {
                method: 'POST',
                headers: {
                    'Content-Type': 'application/json',
                },
                body: JSON.stringify({ name, email, message }),
            });

            if (response.ok) {
                alert('Message sent successfully!');
                $('#contactFormElement')[0].reset();
            } else {
                alert('Failed to send message.');
            }
        });
    });
</script>

</html>